metadata.name: GOW Lottery
metadata.description: The GOW Lottery is a collection of 3000 NFTs created by the Gang Of Women. Behind these 3000 NFTs there are two winning tickets that will make you win a Mutant Ape Club NFT or a World Of Women NFT. Participating in the lottery also guarantees you a WL spot for the Gang Of Women collection that is coming soon. The winners will be drawn live. Who will be the winners of the two tickets? Let's find out!
